{"tid":1509231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［點解街頭冇哂文宣] 想幫下手既入黎","createTime":"2019-08-26T18:36:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T02:06:10.000Z","uid":261649,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"93f80a4b3b60c3df043e0466b9e50355aa19778c","tid":1509231,"uid":261649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T18:36:04.000Z","msg":"其實香港人真係好善忘<br />\n同埋日日咁多事都好易麻木<br />\n<br />\n大家想黎緊行動成功既話<br />\n依幾日文宣好重要<br />\n香港人冇左團火就冇<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有三個方向文宣要煲<br />\n<br />\n1. 黑警啲罪行<br />\nE.g 開真槍踢人、醫院酷刑、新屋嶺私刑<br />\n<br />\n2. 將來行動<br />\nE.g 8.31民陣遊行、9.1無限期機場、學生罷學<br />\n<br />\n3. 良心消費<br />\nE.g 黃藍商店</span></span><br />\n<br />\n需要大量人係街頭宣傳<br />\n唔好fb分享下就話宣傳左<br />\n同溫層宣傳係冇用<br />\n好多番工既示威者、街坊唔用fb/連登<br />\n我地要將訊息傳比佢地<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔一定要派傳單，拎住個牌企街都得<br />\n想要圖、印刷地方PM我</span><br />\n<br />\n點解熱門一個機場、清算港鐵po都冇架屌<br />\n幫我推啦"},{"pid":"8f27cf077f12c7baa3746962d38619692761aca2","tid":1509231,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T18:36:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrhjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=fdce2296\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrhjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=94ce773a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHl